---
/** Safe-sleep setup: what belongs in the crib (almost nothing) and what doesn't. */
---

<figure class="diagram">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 720 340" width="100%" fill="none" role="img" aria-label="Safe sleep setup: baby on back on a firm flat mattress in a sleep sack, crib in the parents' room, with no pillows, bumpers, loose blankets, or stuffed toys.">
    <rect width="720" height="340" rx="16" fill="var(--sage-wash, #E8F0E3)" />

    <!-- Crib -->
    <g>
      <rect x="48" y="88" width="264" height="14" rx="7" fill="var(--sage-deep, #557B4B)" />
      <rect x="48" y="216" width="264" height="14" rx="7" fill="var(--sage-deep, #557B4B)" />
      {Array.from({ length: 9 }).map((_, i) => (
        <rect x={62 + i * 30} y="100" width="8" height="118" rx="4" fill="var(--sage, #6B9A5F)" opacity="0.55" />
      ))}
      <!-- Firm flat mattress -->
      <rect x="56" y="196" width="248" height="22" rx="6" fill="#FFFFFF" />
      <!-- Baby on back: head + sleep sack -->
      <circle cx="110" cy="180" r="17" fill="var(--butter, #F2DFA8)" />
      <path d="M130 168 L226 172 Q240 181 226 191 L130 193 Q124 181 130 168 Z" fill="var(--leaf, #8FBC85)" />
      <circle cx="104" cy="176" r="2.2" fill="var(--ink, #3D443A)" />
      <circle cx="114" cy="176" r="2.2" fill="var(--ink, #3D443A)" />
      <path d="M105 185 q5 3 10 0" stroke="var(--ink, #3D443A)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" />
      <!-- legs of crib -->
      <rect x="52" y="230" width="10" height="52" rx="4" fill="var(--sage-deep, #557B4B)" />
      <rect x="298" y="230" width="10" height="52" rx="4" fill="var(--sage-deep, #557B4B)" />
    </g>
    <text x="180" y="308" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-body)" font-size="15" font-weight="700" fill="var(--sage-deep, #557B4B)">In your room for the first 6 months</text>

    <!-- Checklist -->
    <g font-family="var(--font-body)" font-size="16">
      <text x="368" y="72" font-size="14" font-weight="800" letter-spacing="1.5" fill="var(--sage-deep, #557B4B)">ALWAYS</text>
      {[
        'On the back, every sleep',
        'Firm, flat mattress — fitted sheet only',
        'Sleep sack instead of blankets',
      ].map((label, i) => (
        <g>
          <circle cx="380" cy={94 + i * 34} r="10" fill="var(--sage, #6B9A5F)" />
          <path d={`M375 ${94 + i * 34} l3.5 3.5 6.5 -7`} stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          <text x="402" y={100 + i * 34} fill="var(--ink, #3D443A)">{label}</text>
        </g>
      ))}

      <text x="368" y="214" font-size="14" font-weight="800" letter-spacing="1.5" fill="var(--rose-deep, #C98B8B)">NEVER IN THE CRIB</text>
      {[
        'Pillows, bumpers, positioners',
        'Loose blankets or stuffed toys',
      ].map((label, i) => (
        <g>
          <circle cx="380" cy={236 + i * 34} r="10" fill="var(--rose, #E8B4B4)" />
          <path d={`M376 ${232 + i * 34} l8 8 M384 ${232 + i * 34} l-8 8`} stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
          <text x="402" y={242 + i * 34} fill="var(--ink, #3D443A)">{label}</text>
        </g>
      ))}
    </g>
  </svg>
  <figcaption>The whole safe-sleep setup: back to sleep, bare crib, your room. (AAP &amp; CPS guidance.)</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .diagram {
    margin: var(--space-2) 0;
  }

  .diagram figcaption {
    margin-top: var(--space-half);
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
</style>
